Umndeni walesi sihlabani ebesidume umhlaba wonke, wadalula ngoLwesine esithangamini sabezindaba eGoli ukuthi ngeke uludalule usuku lomngcwabo. Umfowabo kaHugh, uLesetja Masekela wathi kuhlelwe izinkonzo zesikhumbuzo ezahlukene ukuze abalandeli bakaBra Hugh bazomhlonipha. Wakubeka ukuthi umngcwabo uzohanjelwa umndeni, izihlobo nezimenywa ebezisebenza naye endimeni yomculo. Umphakathi nabezindaba kwavela ukuthi abavunyelwe enkonzweni. Umthombo weSolezwe ongashayi eceleni, uthe konke kuzokwenziwa ngoLwesibili. “Umngcwabo kuhlelwe ukuthi ube ngoLwesibili okuwusuku azolothiswa ngalo,” kuchaza umthombo ngamafuphi. Izolo elinye iphephandaba lesiNgisi liveze ukuthi le ngqalabutho ilothiswe ngoLwesihlanu. Umthombo uthe abomndeni bazokwenza inkonzo yokumvalelisa endaweni eyimfihlo bese eyolothiswa. Izolo bekunenkonzo yokugcina kaHugh eNyuvesi yaseJohannesburg, ekhempasini yaseSoweto. Udadewabo kaHugh, uBarbara ubonge odokotela abebesiza lesi sihlabani sisesibhedlela. Udadewabo uthe bayazi ukuthi abantu bakuleli bebemthanda umfowabo, uthando abalukhombisile esedlulile lubenze bathobeka. Ubonge wonke amaciko asebenze nomfowabo. UBarbara uchaze umfowabo ngokuthi ubengumuntu obengananazi ukulikhuluma njengoba linjalo iqiniso. UNgqongqoshe wamaSiko namaCiko kuzwelonke, uNathi Mthethwa uthe ngeke amlibale uHugh.